orn 1959) – Israeli-American rabbi and defender of Palestinian human rights * [[Uri Avnery]] (1923–2018) – Israeli writer and founder of [[Gush Shalom]] * [[Mubarak Awad]] (born 1943) – Palestinian–American advocate of nonviolent resistance, founder of the [[Palestinian Centre for the Study of Nonviolence]] * [[Ali Abu Awwad]] (born 1972) – Palestinian peace activist from [[Beit Ummar]], founder of ''al-Tariq'' ("the way") * [[Ayo Ayoola-Amale]] (born 1970) – Nigerian conflict resolution professional, ombudsman, peace builder and poet
